keys used in CTR mode or CBC mode is allowed by the Compliance Rules.
MP4-based formats are recommended. CMAF is the preferred MP4-based format for
PlayReady Clients, Windows 10, and Xbox One.
Microsoft supports the two common encryption schemes which have broad industry
